<plot>Mother and son, are running away from abusing husband and father. A young couple are about to became parents. A little girl is on her way to school. A stressed business man. A broken hearted girl. All together on a train journey, telling the life story of an old couple. These characters carry a heavy load on their shoulders: their life stories. Their load is full of pain, betrayal, angst, impotence to change, search for love, moments of happiness, giving up and, always last, hope.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?609675</url></doc>
